title: Quiz AWS
description: Quiz AWS is a web application that contains a bank of questions on AWS Practitioner to test technical knowledge.

title: AFTAS
description: Aftas is a web application designed to modernize the management of competitions. It allows for efficient administration by the club and effective management by the jury, providing a responsive and user-friendly platform.

title: Come2Play
description: Come2Play is a web application that allows users to search for, book, and review football fields.

title: Chess
description: Chess is played on an 8x8 board, with 16 pieces per player: 8 pawns, 2 rooks, 2 knights, 2 bishops, 1 queen, and 1 king.
